<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <%- include('./head'); %>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header><%- include('./header'); %></header>
    <main>
      <div><%- include('./tabs'); %></div>
      <div class="container">
        <!-- Hero section -->
        <div
          class="row bg-image p-5 text-center shadow-1-strong rounded mb-5 text-white align-items-center"
          style="background-image: url('../images/valopuu.png'); height: 50vh"
        >
          <h1 class="mb-3 h3 animated-text">
            Welcome to the Karelia Developer Portal <br /><br />
            Platform where you can innovate and create smart campus solutions.
          </h1>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 50px"></div>
        <!-- Info section -->
        <div class="row fade-in">
          <div class="col-md-10 offset-md-1 text-center">
            <h2 class="mb-4">What is the Karelia Developer Portal?</h2>
            <p>
              The Karelia Developer Portal is part of
              <strong>Karelia UAS's Smart Campus initiative</strong>. This
              platform brings students, teachers, and partners together by
              showcasing student-created digital projects in one place.
            </p>

            <h4 class="mt-4">For Students</h4>
            <p>
              Add links to your GitHub repositories on the
              <strong>Apps, Libs & Repos</strong> page to share your work with
              others. Discover what your peers are building and let teachers,
              fellow students, and potential employers see your creations.
            </p>
            <p>
              Want hands-on practice? Register and log in to generate your own
              <strong>API token</strong> and start experimenting with
              <strong>Karelia's APIs</strong>. Perfect for learning modern web
              development and software production.
            </p>

            <h4 class="mt-4">For Organizations</h4>
            <p>
              Propose a student project and get real results. You'll gain access
              to new ideas, research insights, and fresh perspectives, all while
              providing students with valuable experience and increasing your
              visibility among future professionals.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- End of Info section -->
      </div>
    </main>
    <!-- space before footer -->
    <div style="margin-top: 50px"></div>
    <footer><%- include('./footer'); %></footer>
  </body>
</html>
